Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:15.94,OP English,,0,0,0,,And I'm already blue. What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:22.68,OP English,,0,0,0,,I'd rather wear my summer clothes. ←So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:25.98,OP English,,0,0,0,,3 pics incoming! That's a toughie to pick! Ooh {\fe128\fscx85\fscy85}☆ {The star doesn't render in the kara font!}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:29.98,OP English,,0,0,0,,Just work it! (Yeah!) To the limit! (Yeah!) My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngaah~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and start already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have someone solve this problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You just picked on me last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,E-eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Urk...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my English textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go borrow it from Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Her class already had English today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You should check it the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, you forget a lot of things, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata, you never forget your textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, I'm pretty good with those kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave all my textbooks at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not good with them at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't review anything if your textbooks are at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't study at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you don't even bring them home until the day before a test...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kona-chan, you're good at cramming the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why I forget my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In your case, we don't call that 'forgetting.'
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't have the motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can I see your Japanese homework from last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Already!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're in the same class with her, why don't you just look at Miyuki's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san is such a good person that it's actually hard to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of do, but I'm still not convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she tardy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was helping someone out, and it caused me to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We usually do things together...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just couldn't leave him alone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He was nice enough to say, 'Don't worry about me... we can disband.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But with five people in the group, having only one parting leaves a bad aftertaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention we've been partying together for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all help each other out in times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to have good friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you stayed up late last night playing an internet game?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been playing after I dropped, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this... late again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl bumped into me in front of the shopping mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that girl suddenly grabbed my hand and started running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I listened to what she had to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She had apparently stolen a Taiyaki and was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought to myself, 'Why do I have to be involved in this?'
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't have much of a choice at that point, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In an attempt to hide, we ran into the nearest café and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uguu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can think of so many things to say right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I probably shouldn't say them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As a teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uuu~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught a summer cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Izumi, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I'm really sorry but I feel sick today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What, been playing too many games again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times are you going to use the same excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I would like to be absent today because I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you going to tell me you caught a summer cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The rainy season is over and the weather's good right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, stop saying you're tired and get your butt over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So yesterday, I totally got treated like the boy who cried wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You had it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, do you feel better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My fever's gone, but my throat still hurts a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, you breathe through your mouth, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure sometimes people breathe through their mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it usually through the nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but, perhaps Kona-chan breathes through her throat more than her nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cold virus enters through your mouth, you'll get a sore throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it enters through your nose, you'll get a runny nose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get a sore throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that because the chances of the virus entering your mouth are really high?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like this, it's better to just call for Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,About today's birthday party, do you want to do it at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot I can't even take a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm baking cookies at my place right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa and company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't downplay me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami-san and Tsukasa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And well, this is something boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pair of earrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it a lot of through, but I still had a hard time deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall offer my presents too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Brigade Leader arm-band.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to put this thing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would fit you perfectly, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It would probably look better on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To Heart!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really expensive you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of it when you wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make the both of us cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that much different from our uniforms anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'd be troubling if it were too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it sure would... and when it stinks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's someone else's birthday, so why don't you hold back a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These cookies that Tsukasa made sure taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it with her this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was learning as I went along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I tasted some 'good' ones and some 'not so good' ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this one is Kagami's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're all here already, why don't you guys have some cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And so Kagami worked very hard for one day of the year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:07:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you ever get into debates about how to cut a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, if you're cutting it into many pieces, what would you do with the strawberry on top...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Or who gets to eat the chocolate on the plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you like the chocolate, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't cut it straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel the moe when Kagami makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Itadakima~su.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My strawberry is so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there cake on my face or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just discovered another one of your attractions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really look like him now so stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost summer vacation again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean, pools and summer festivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I miss anything else that's important?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,*Pause*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that twice-a-year event...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The grand opening of a battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,None other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Comiket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no no no... that's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess there are events for all sorts of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Go competitions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, do you have anything you do every summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have plans to go travel abroad again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,'Again this year...'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she just say 'again?'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn bourgeoisie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a type of yogurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you started working at a cosplay cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you have to have good style to work in places like those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was pretty worried since I didn't exactly have big breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But a certain game once said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,'Small breasts are a status!'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,'A rare quality!'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So it said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, you can look at it that way too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm pretty valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to know how she can have so much confidence because of games...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm okay too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Finals are coming up soon, so are you going to be okay playing games all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you would redirect some of that passion to studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your grades would go up a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's that easily influenced...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A game that promotes studying may have a huge effect on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they do have Moe Drill for the DS and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been a lot of crimes committed by juveniles recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you interview the neighbors, they all seem to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,'He was always a quiet kid, so I never could imagine him doing something like that.'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that just means you can't judge someone on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you commit some sort of crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,'I was certain she would some something sooner or later.'
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot that I don't feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But you come up with all sorts of reasons year-round to say, 'I don't feel like doing anything.'
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How's studying for finals coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cleaning up my room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you really feel like cleaning when you know tests are coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you're feeling, but just do your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I should do a little today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a 30-minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's time already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 30 more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,30 more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving Nagato such long screen times... are they slacking off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,****kan hasn't been too impressive lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's getting bashed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, it's already 2 o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't get into the mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to sleep early and do it tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wake up at 5 AM...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sleep for a whole three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I wasted time reading manga and watching anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so like you, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata, your game and manga preferences are quite esoteric.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You read shounen manga and mainly play bishoujo games, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to see my dad read manga and play games a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was probably influenced by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching him since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand the shounen manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But playing gal-games and bishoujo-games in front of your little daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of dad would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,With both of you like that, doesn't your mom say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a mom, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She died when I was really small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm always the one doing the chores around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet I'm a lot better than you at doing them, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say something unnecessary at a time when it's inappropriate to joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, you're good at cooking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm good or not, but I like to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Miyuki-san is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks really rich, so maybe she's not good at those sorts or things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I only help now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not too good at chores like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miyuki-san, you're too good at everything else, so your standards are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't take this girl's 'not good' literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how sensei is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She lives alone, but I have a pretty sloppy image of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, even if you can't cook, you can still manage to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There are convenience stores and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as well as an average person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't joke with such a straight face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I loaned my dictionary to Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, I'm sorry but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have my dictionary back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was cleaning my room for a change-of-mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone at my part-time job is deciding on a new summer menu right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did you give up on your tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's hot, people think of spicy things...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about we have super-spicy ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you make a menu that's more cafe like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, a super-spicy parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop with the off-the-top-of-your-head ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't our school have any swimming classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we have a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of saved by that though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I can't open my eyes under water...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't swim much either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh how I wish I had your 'weaknesses.'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the summer Comp-Matsuri is opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, this was the reason I started working.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A festival huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything seems so nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you bringing up old thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's really exhilarating to get caught up in the moment with the other customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it make you feel that together you're making the festival livelier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just use a little of that enthusiasm for school, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to fall asleep just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll read a book or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I just bought one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did I not fall asleep, it's already morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm starting to fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why you have to turn the power off in the priority seats...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of pacemakers and stuff, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you talk on your cell phone while on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that because it's rude to talk when there are other passengers around you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't there still some loud people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not taking into account people who are talking on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,During the summer festival, are you going to work at the shrine like you did for the New Year's first shrine visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I decided not to do that this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's almost that season again, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you on a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was because I was studying for tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I weighed myself yesterday, I was lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought that maybe it was okay after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My weight's returned, but it's not something for which I've yearned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you let your guard down and kept snacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, was that a poem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only ate a bit here and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of kilos won't even affect your appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so worried about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why women are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were supposed to be a woman too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oha-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's started again this week: Lucky Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you all been taking care of yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Always at 120% cheerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogami Akira here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This time{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyoro~n!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the assistant, Shiraishi Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just cut me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't 'Not an Errand Boy,' so try to do better at your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to get fired that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try harder... I'll try harder... I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a very important announcement for you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The 'Make Akira Look Better' plan from November's Comptiq.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have this many postcards from everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, wasn't there another person included in that plan besides you, Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for sending in so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira's mammothly happy-pii.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they'll understand 80's jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we'll present an idea that was selected after rigorous screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Any of these will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,From Saitama-ken, this is Sappishi-Cherry-san's 'Akira look better plan!'
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami-san's twintails look really good on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you try out twintails too, Akira-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Twintails, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds really{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uuu~n lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Long hair is a woman's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you split that in two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How graceful would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you do it or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's possible with your short hair, Akira-sama--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, it's not all about letting your hair grow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's really heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost visible, therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pain to shampoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama, it's just barely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not that popular nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys say they like girls with long hair, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they have any idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's something someone in the series would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time and money we put into maintaining this hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you, Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked so hard and no one seems to notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwaa~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to say goodbye already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, if you want to find out what would happen if Akira had twintails...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to the homepage, or we can talk about it again on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-pii!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What was with your attitude back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You interrupted me so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You were pissed that I didn't mention you in the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,O-oh, that's not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just worried that they might not know who Nori-P was, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,T-then let's go with a different feel next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I heard they're doing a Shiraishi Minoru audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't heard of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay for you to audition, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sing anything, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm limited to anime songs, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You sing so well with so many different voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the iron rule of anime songs to follow the originals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll sing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, what are you going to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the title earlier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, you don't know this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, you shouldn't be talking about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just watching this drama together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer the movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you some sort of old geezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:46.99,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:47.82,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:51.62,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan is the best at \Nsinging out of the whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next week's Lucky Star is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that 'Golden Week' comes from all the extra money that the movie theaters make during this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Next week: A Famous Shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
